
> These learning goals will have to be updated when we decide what will be included and excluded from the introduction. For now I have created
list of all possible goals that can flow from our current set of ideas in the google doc shared in #intro on Slack.

*After completion of the module the student is able to...*

*Understand the historical development of the concept 'sustainability' and its current connotations.
*Give an overview of key 'sustainability' literature.
*Analyse a sustainability issue through a systems thinking approach
*Explain the relevance of interdisciplinary research.
